                               <p style="text-align:justify;    font-size: 1rem;">Sports is an integral part of total curriculum, hence the school provides all the basic facilities for development of positive sports environment. Magadhians, through their participation in diverse extracurricular activities & sports not only discover their talents but also earn recognition and set examples of excellence at state and national levels. The school considers education a life-long process. The goal is to inculcate in the students a love for learning and a desire to excel at every level.</p>
                     
